title: The Von Haessler Doctrine Special Edition S6/E019 - Little Guy With Big Microphone
description: Join Eric, Clark Howard, B98.5's Tad Lemire, Comedian Costaki Economopoulos, and the Doctrinaires as they chat from Super Bowl LIII's Media Center about the big game, Winter Storm Jayden, the 'M' word, and much more! "Sponsored by Mr. Mister Mosquito Control"
